  "ja539:39.3": "Pahāya pabbajissāmi,",
  "ja539:39.4": "taṁ kudāssu bhavissati.",
  "ja539:40.1": "Kadāhaṁ antepuraṁ rammaṁ,",
  "ja539:40.2": "sucigandhaṁ manoramaṁ;",
  "ja539:40.3": "Pahāya pabbajissāmi,",
